metadata.name: Business walk
metadata.description:
After walking the streets of Rome all day long, I saw this group of business people walking down the square with nice backlight so I took the shot. This is the best shot of that day, if not of the whole trip.

Location: Piazza Colonna, Rome, Italy

This photo is part of the "Glimpse of Life" collection, a series of photographs capturing ordinary and extraordinary life of people from all around the world.
